  "description": "A group of people are gathered around a roaring bonfire at night. The fire is the central point of the image, casting a warm, orange glow on the faces and bodies of those surrounding it. Individuals are visible, seated closely together, creating a sense of camaraderie and warmth. Several people are illuminated by the firelight, showing their faces and upper bodies while others are silhouetted against the bright flames. The background is dark, suggesting a remote or outdoor location. The overall scene evokes a feeling of togetherness, storytelling, and the primal comfort of fire.",
